  {
    "type": "EXEGETICAL (ORIGINAL LANGUAGES)",
    "name": "Pulpit Commentary",
    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "cmt_sub_title",
        "text": "Verse 12.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " - ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "cmt_word",
        "text": "And it came to pass, when Ben-hadad",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " [Heb. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "accented",
        "text": "he",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "] ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "cmt_word",
        "text": "heard this message",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " [Heb. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "accented",
        "text": "word",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "], ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "cmt_word",
        "text": "as he was drinking, he and the kings in the pavilions",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " [Heb. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "accented",
        "text": "booths",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". The word shows that, in lieu of tents, kings and generals on an expedition sometimes used leafy huts, like those of Israel (",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Leviticus 23:34, 42",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "). Such booths, it is said, are still erected on military expeditions in the East], ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "cmt_word",
        "text": "that he said unto his servants, Set yourselves in array",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " [Heb. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "hebrew",
        "text": "שִׂימוּ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " one short, decisive word. His indignation and astonishment were too great for more. We might perhaps render \"Form.\" Cf. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "1 Samuel 11:11",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "; ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Joshua 8:2, 13",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "; ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Job 1:17",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "; ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Ezekiel 23:24",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". It cannot mean ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "greek",
        "text": "οἰκοδομήσατε χάρακα",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " (LXX.)] ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "cmt_word",
        "text": "And they set themselves in array",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " [or ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "accented",
        "text": "formed",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". Again one word, which is more spirited and graphic, and conveys that the command was instantly obeyed] ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "cmt_word",
        "text": "against the city.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " 1 Kings 20:12",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "",
        "children": []
      }
    ]
